390
00:20:51,882 --> 00:20:53,102
No.

391
00:20:53,469 --> 00:20:54,629
I should beat him up first.

392
00:20:54,710 --> 00:20:55,967
After that, I'll splash his house with paint.

393
00:20:55,991 --> 00:20:58,162
