404
00:21:24,162 --> 00:21:25,382
He's fine.

405
00:21:26,681 --> 00:21:29,181
He won't miss out on such a good sadfishing opportunity.

406
00:21:31,441 --> 00:21:32,762
I'll call Cheng Xi.

407
00:21:37,044 --> 00:21:38,939
