421
00:22:13,602 --> 00:22:14,802
Yao Yao.

422
00:22:14,944 --> 00:22:16,762
Did Wu Jun keep hanging up on Yao Yao?

423
00:22:17,378 --> 00:22:18,922
(Cheng Xi, how are you?)

424
00:22:19,481 --> 00:22:20,701
I'm fine.

425
00:22:20,782 --> 00:22:22,922
