474
00:24:32,170 --> 00:24:33,790
Guys, please take your seats.

475
00:24:35,314 --> 00:24:37,600
The two parties involved today, which are Ms. Sun and Mr. Shi,

476
00:24:37,624 --> 00:24:39,457
