578
00:29:21,640 --> 00:29:23,721
Even now, you wish to push the blame on Ms. Sun?

579
00:29:23,921 --> 00:29:26,177
She already did everything she could, but you're still guilt-tripping her.

580
00:29:26,201 --> 00:29:28,921
