00:30:53,046 --> 00:30:55,367
(Hello, everyone. I'm Cheng Xi.)

615
00:30:55,595 --> 00:30:57,082
(I'm Deng Ming's ex-wife.)

616
00:30:57,927 --> 00:31:00,727
